title: Lilly Wood & The Prick and Robin Schulz - Prayer In C (Singl
description:
"Prayer in C" is a song by French alternative pop and folk duo Lilly Wood & The Prick. It was originally released in 2010 on their album, Invincible Friends. German electronic producer Robin Schulz remixed the song and in June 2014, he released it as a single. The remix propelled the song to success across Europe, topping the charts in Austria, Germany, Luxembourg, Switzerland and France.

04:17, 320 kbps, 2014, Tonspiel - Warner music
